OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1773486371
OL,3,CMan, 49, arrested as police launch
OL,4,Cmurder probe into death of a man in
OL,5,Chis 50s
OL,7,FA man has been arrested after the
OL,8,Fdeath of a man in County Durham.
OL,10,FPolice were called to Dent Street in
OL,11,FShildon on Tuesday 10 March after 1pm,
OL,12,Ffollowing reports that a man had been
OL,13,Fassaulted.
OL,15,FA man in his 50s was taken to James
OL,16,FCook University Hospital having
OL,17,Fsuffered serious injuries. He was
OL,18,Fpronounced dead shortly after arrival.
OL,20,FA murder investigation was shortly
OL,21,Flaunched by Durham Constabulary.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
