PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1773486371
OL,3,CMan, 49, arrested as police launch
OL,4,Cmurder probe into death of a man in
OL,5,Chis 50s
OL,7,FOfficers have arrested a 49-year-old
OL,8,Fman, where he remains in police
OL,9,Fcustody.
OL,11,FA police presence is expected in the
OL,12,Farea while investigations continue,
OL,13,FDurham Constabulary have said.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Sharon
OL,16,FAlderson said: "We understand that
OL,17,Fthis incident will have caused shock
OL,18,Fto the community, and our thoughts are
OL,19,Fwith the victim's loved ones during
OL,20,Fthis difficult time.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1773486371
OL,3,CMan, 49, arrested as police launch
OL,4,Cmurder probe into death of a man in
OL,5,Chis 50s
OL,7,F"While there will be an increased
OL,8,Fpolice presence in the area as we
OL,9,Fcarry out our enquiries, I can
OL,10,Freassure the community of Shildon that
OL,11,Fwe believe this to be an isolated
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,F"I'd like to thank residents for their
OL,15,Fsupport and co-operation while our
OL,16,Finvestigation is carried out.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
