PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1773486371
OL,3,CMan, 49, arrested as police launch
OL,4,Cmurder probe into death of a man in
OL,5,Chis 50s
OL,7,F"A team of officers are currently
OL,8,Fworking to establish the circumstances
OL,9,Fsurrounding the incident and we are
OL,10,Fkeen to hear from anyone who witnessed
OL,11,Fthe incident who has not yet spoken to
OL,12,Fus."
OL,14,FAnyone with information which can help
OL,15,Fpolice with their investigation is
OL,16,Fasked to call Durham Constabulary on
OL,17,F101, quoting incident reference 209 of
OL,18,F10 March.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
